description: Conveniently located near shops, restaurants, M Street beach, parks, and schools, this turnkey condo will satisfy the most discerning buyer. The first floor offers an open concept floor plan with a state of the art kitchen, dining area, and living room with a gas fireplace and access to the porch. The first floor also has a full bathroom and two bedrooms. The second floor offers a large bedroom, half bathroom, and access to the private roof deck with downtown Boston views. Recent improvements include a brand new HVAC system, a new hot water heater, all new exterior siding, and a new rooftop deck. Low monthly HOA’s further enhance the appeal of this lovely condo. Move right in and enjoy.
